metadata.name: Lynn Wistar
metadata.description:
Airdate: 2/24/2022

Character Illustration by: SavazQ#4727

Story by Contestants: emikusano#5930, devin#2565, Wailoaloa#7613, jayr#6593

Show Hosted by: rogden#5480

Story: Lynn's bird mentors, the Thunder Tyrants, are missing. She has a premonition of the Ostrich Emperor, Valen Ironwing. Lynn visits Ironwing's Kingdom, but the annual Ostrich Ball is in full swing. Identified as an intruder, Lynn is challenged by Ironwing to a formal dance challenge. Lynn remembers her mentors' training, and performs the Sword Dance she learned as a child. Ironwing spits up rainbow yogurt, but Lynn's feet are lightning fast. She earns the respect of the kingdom. Power and grace win hearts.
